org.jhove2.core.source
Interface MeasurableSource

All Superinterfaces:
Comparable<Source>, Reportable, Source
All Known Implementing Classes:
ByteStreamSource, FileSource, URLSource
public interface MeasurableSource
extends Source

Interface for measurable Source units, that is, those that have a knowable size.

slabrams
